summary: THE FAILURE OF A FOURTH STAGE HYDRAULIC CYLINDER CAUSED THE FRAMELESS DUMP TRAILER TO FALL DOWN AND FORWARD CAUSING INJURIES TO THE DRIVER AND DAMAGE TO THE VEHICLE (HYDRAULIC CYLINDER MANUFACTURED BY PARKER HANNIFIN CORPORATION UTILIZED IN A 2001 FRAMELESS DUMP TRAILER MANUFACTURER'S BY EAST MANUFACTURING COMPANY).  THE CONSUMER REQUESTS INFO ON SIMILAR ACCIDENTS THAT MAY HAVE OCCURRED FROM THIS SAME COMPONENT.  *SCC
